We wish to know how many e-petitions have been:
a. created (step 1);
b. submitted and acknowledged (step 2);
c. approved (step 3);
d. made live (step 4); and,
e. closed.

Please list on this website all e-petitions that have reached step 2 (with dates on which they were received) but had not been approved (step 3) by 30 November 2006.
